Vallavanukku Pullum Aayudham  is a 2014 Indian Tamil-language action comedy film directed by Srinath and released by Studio Green on 9 May 2014. A remake of S. S. Rajamouli's successful Telugu film Maryada Ramanna (2010) which was based on Buster Keaton's Our Hospitality (1923),[1] the film was jointly produced by PVP Cinema and Santhanam, who also played the lead role in it, alongside newcomer Ashna Zaveri. snippet.title: Anuv Jain - AFSOS ft. AP Dhillon (Official Visualizer)
snippet.description:
Listen to Anuv Jain - 'Afsos' ft. AP Dhillon on all streaming platforms - https://umgindia.lnk.to/Afsos
#anuvjain #afsos #apdhillon 

For inquiries - anuvjain.work@gmail.com
Instagram - @anuvjain
Manager- aayushman@representmgmt.in

Audio Credits:
Composer: Anuv Jain, Shinda Kahlon, AP Dhillon
Lyrics: Anuv Jain, Shinda Kahlon, AP Dhillon, Reeka Jain
Music Producers: Angad Bahra, Anuv Jain, Luca Mauti, AP Dhillon, Brendan Rogers
Atmos Mix: Pixl

Project Managers - Aayushman Sinha, Tanvi Seth, Sidhantha Jain, Murtuza Gadiwala, Madhura Rumde, Anirudh Voletti
Team: Shirsodhi Banerjee, Mihika Bansal, Bhavya Killa

Lyric Video by Hariom Verma (LazyOm)
Special Mention to the team at Dreaming in Digital

Artwork: Kartik Kher, LazyOm, AK Digitals
Shout Out to Fleck Media for capturing an incredible moment

AFSOS (Lyrics)

A 1

Haan 
Teri yaadan yaadan 
Teri yaadan le ke betha 
Kai raatan raatan

Par aaj
Ena raatan picho
Meinu sab sach nazar ae aunda
Kivein akhan akhan?

B 1

Jo guroor si 
Oh fizool si 
Meinu aaj pata laga 
Ki kasoor si 

Mere dil de noor 
Main si mash-hoor 
Tenu karta dur 
Oh, bekasoor!

Kinj gairan nu 
Main apna mann 
Mileya mere apne nu 
Gair ban

Eh taan zaroor 
Dil karta choor
Tera

C 1 

Te haan
Main duniya vekhi 
Tere dil nu vekh na paya 
Main jhalla jhalla 

Karda si
Wadeya nawan di
Gallan gallan

Hun ethe
Marda janda 
Main kalla kalla

A 2

Hun kyun 
Afsos hoya?
Hun ki fayeda?
Milna ni
Je chahaan chahaan

Main hun
Ghadiya de hath te
Kivein modha 
Rukh samay da 
Te rahaan rahaan?

D 

Chand pal do pal 
Teri sunda battan je 

Tere nal hi 
Sab katda rattan je 

Tere hanju dekhda 
Vich barsattan je

Kitte karda teh 
Eh dil di vattan je 

B 2

Kaisi shaam si
Tere naam si 
Jo padheya na main
Ki pegham si?

Main hairan si
Naadan si
Kis gallon meri jaan
Pareshan si?

Tenu hasde vekh ke
Baar baar
Tenu puchi na main kadey tere
Dil di saar

Tera intezar, 
Meri samjho baar 
Kidda katey ne tu din metho 
Haar haar?

C 2

Haan
Jo pyaar si tera
Thoda vi samajh na paya 
Main jhalla jhalla 

Haan
Eh dil pachtave 
Tere bin hun reh na pave 
Eh kalla kalla

A 3

Hun kyun 
Afsos hoya?
Hun ki fayeda?
Milna ni
Je chahaan chahaan

Main hun
Ghadiya de hath te
Kivein modha 
Rukh samay da 
Te rahaan rahaan?

Te rahaan rahaan
Te rahaan rahaan

snippet.title: 1st Test Day 1 | Highlights | Australia Tour Of Sri Lanka | 29th January 2025
snippet.description:
Australia and Sri Lanka faced each other at the Galle International Stadium for the 1st Test match. On day 1, Australia showcased a dominant performance with the bat as they posted 330 runs and lost just 2 wickets in the process. Moreover, Khawaja and Smith both scored centuries and are still unbeaten.
.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.title: SNAIL FRY | NATHAI VARUVAL | Snail Recipe Cooking and Eating in Village | Healthy Village Recipes
snippet.description:
Discover the art of traditional Snail Fry (Nathai Varuval) cooking in the heart of the village! üêå‚ú® This unique recipe combines fresh, locally sourced snails with a blend of aromatic spices, creating a mouthwatering dish that‚Äôs as healthy as it is flavorful.

Watch as we prepare this delicacy from scratch, using simple yet time-tested techniques over a firewood stove. Every step showcases the charm of village cooking, from cleaning the snails to frying them to perfection.

What‚Äôs in the Recipe:

Fresh snails straight from nature
A medley of traditional spices
Gingelly oil and hand-ground masala for authentic flavor

This video is not just about cooking; it celebrates culture, community, and the joy of sharing delicious food. Stay until the end for a delightful tasting session that will leave you craving this wholesome delicacy!

#AjithKumar #Dubai24H #RacingVictory #AjithKumarRacing #Pathikichu #vidaamuyarchi #MotivationalMusic #NeverGiveUp #Perseverance #sonymusicsouth 

In this thrilling video, witness the incredible victory of actor Ajith Kumar at the prestigious Dubai 24H Racing event, where he and his team, Ajith Kumar Racing, delivered a performance for the ages. Driven by sheer determination and unmatched passion, Ajith‚Äôs triumph is a testament to his never-ending perseverance both on and off the track.

This victory is set to the backdrop of Ajith‚Äôs upcoming film Vidamuyarchi, with the motivational track Pathikichu fueling the energy and inspiring everyone who believes in pushing through all obstacles. The song perfectly complements his relentless spirit, making this achievement even more special.

Watch as Ajith‚Äôs journey unfolds, from the intense competition on the racetrack to the emotional victory lap, showing that success is the result of hard work, dedication, and never giving up.

snippet.title: Pre-booked Breakfast On Air India Express!! ‚úàÔ∏èüçΩÔ∏è
snippet.description:
Pre-booked a ‚Çπ650 breakfast on my Air India Express flight from Bengaluru to Delhi‚Äîwas it worth it? First, a little heartbreak‚Äîwhere‚Äôs the iconic artificial waterfall at T2? Anyway, after boarding the new Boeing 737, I found myself in a middle seat with no window (tough life). Took off with a limited outside view and soon, food arrived! T

he masala tea? Too watered down. The cheese omelette? A bit eggy at first but got better. The hara bhara kebab? Surprisingly soft and moist. The baked beans? Classic, soft, and mushy. 

But the real winner? The banana chocolate cake‚Äîdense, balanced, and a big thumbs up! Wrapped it all up with some water before dozing off, only to wake up to great weather in Delhi. Another flight, another meal reviewed‚Äîsubscribe for more food and travel adventures!

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.description:
India celebrates the 76th Republic Day on 26th January 2025. We at Doordarshan extend our warm regards to all Indians in the country as well as abroad. It is the proud privilege of Doordarshan, India's National Broadcaster to LIVE-STREAM the magnificent 76th Republic Day Parade on our official channel on YouTube. www.youtube/DoordarshanNational. Doordarshan has been telecasting the Republic Day Parade LIVE since the early sixties when cameras and equipment had to be taken out of the existing studio for this event! Today, for the tenth consecutive year, we will LIVE-STREAM the Republic Day Parade. Proud Indians and Indophiles from all over the world will be watching, along with our viewers from the freezing climate of Leh to the remotest corners of Kanyakumari, Thank you for always being with us - Friends of Doordarshan. We at Doordarshan extend our warm regards to all Indians in the country as well as abroad. It is the proud privilege of Doordarshan.

How to make canteen style toast sandwich recipe / toast sandwich recipe 

How to make Sandwich Chutney-
In a mixer grinder, add garlic, ginger, coriander, green chilies, mint leaves, lemon juice,bread pieces, chat masala, salt cold water , and churn it well. Don't make it too watery.¬†

Sandwich Stuffing-¬†
In a mixing bowl, add finely chopped onions, carrots, capsicum, add the chutney we made, 1 cup grated cheese, and mix well.¬†

For Sandwich-
Apply soft butter on bread, add the stuffing and spread it evenly. keep another slice of bread on top of it.¬†
Heat the grill pan, apply butter , keep the sandwich & cook until it turns crispy.¬†

How to make canteen style toast sandwich recipe / toast sandwich recipe 

How to make Sandwich Chutney-
In a mixer grinder, add garlic, ginger, coriander, green chilies, mint leaves, lemon juice,bread pieces, chat masala, salt cold water , and churn it well. Don't make it too watery.¬†

Sandwich Stuffing-¬†
In a mixing bowl, add finely chopped onions, carrots, capsicum, add the chutney we made, 1 cup grated cheese, and mix well.¬†

For Sandwich-
Apply soft butter on bread, add the stuffing and spread it evenly. keep another slice of bread on top of it.¬†
Heat the grill pan, apply butter , keep the sandwich & cook until it turns crispy.¬†
